So you have your async and your error
handling, and your event streams,

7
00:00:16.090 --> 00:00:20.000
and we tend to model these
with types like the functors.

8
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.090
So you have your task and
your either, and your this or that.

9
00:00:24.090 --> 00:00:29.520
