17
00:00:53.085 --> 00:00:56.440
So normalizing the effect types

18
00:00:56.440 --> 00:00:59.980
throughout the app is something
that you probably want to do.

19
00:01:01.290 --> 00:01:09.230
I don't think it's necessarily necessary
all the time but, necessarily necessary.

20
00:01:09.230 --> 00:01:13.601
It's just good guiding principle to have
a normalized shape of your effects so

21
00:01:13.601 --> 00:01:17.900
you end up making maybe an app monad,
and everything falls into that.

22
00:01:17.900 --> 00:01:19.560
And so everything kind of composes.

23
00:01:19.560 --> 00:01:21.020
And there's different
strategies as we'll see,

24
